# ── Static build mode (default) ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Notes are compiled from the filesystem at build time.
# No environment variables needed for static mode.

# ── API mode (Cloudflare Workers) ────────────────────────────────────────────
# When set, the site fetches notes from your Worker at runtime.
# Uncomment and set to your Worker URL to enable API mode.
#
# VITE_GARDEN_API_URL=https://digital-garden-api.your-name.workers.dev
